These are Puzzles for 2x4 Level 3

.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-1::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: spy, comedy, action, superhero
The people use 4 different means of transport: bus, snowmobile, quad-bike, boat
1. the person watching superhero movies is on the left of the person watching spy movies##1
2. the person watching spy movies is on the right of the person watching superhero movies##1
3. the person driving the snowmobile is on the far left or far right##3
4. the person watching action movies is on the right of the person driving the quad-bike##1
5. the person driving the boat is between the person driving the snowmobile and the person driving the quad-bike##2
6. the person watching superhero movies is the person driving the bus##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2     |    3    |    4     |
| Movie-Genre   | superhero | spy     | action | comedy |
| Transport     | bus     | quad-bike | boat  | snowmobile      |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-2::.
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: classical, d&b, punk, country
The people use 4 different means of transport: skateboard, boat, bike, subway
1. the fan of d&b is on the left of the person driving the boat##1
2. the person driving the subway is on the far left or far right##3
3. the fan of country is on the left of the person driving the subway##1
4. the person driving the subway is on the right of the person driving the boat##1
5. the fan of punk is on the far right##1
6. the person driving the skateboard is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |     2      |     3      |   4   |
| Music-Genre   | classical | d&b    | country     | punk  |
| Transport     | skateboard    | bike | boat | subway |

