.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-3::.
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: disco, ambient, trance, d&b
4 different pets are kept: hamster, dog, bird, frog
1. the owner of the frog is on the left or right of the fan of ambient##3
2. the fan of ambient is on the far left##1
3. the owner of the bird is on the left of the fan of d&b##1
4. the owner of the hamster is on the left or right of the fan of disco##3
5. the owner of the bird is on the right of the fan of trance##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |   2   |   3    |  4   |
| Music-Genre   | ambient   | trance   | disco  | d&b |
| Pet           | dog | frog | bird | hamster  |

