.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-4::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: reading, sudoku, hiking, puzzles
There are 4 different nationalities: thai, mexican, spanish, malaysian
1. the malaysian is on the left of the person who's hobby is hiking##1
2. the person who's hobby is puzzles is between the person who's hobby is reading and the spanish##2
3. the person who's hobby is puzzles is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is hiking##3
4. the spanish is on the left or right of the malaysian##3
5. the person who's hobby is reading is on the right of the person who's hobby is sudoku##1
6. the thai is on the right of the mexican##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2      |    3    |    4     |
| Hobby         | sudoku | reading | puzzles | hiking  |
| Nationality   | mexican  | thai   | malaysian  | spanish |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-5::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: mirinda, cola, lemonade, sprite
The people have 4 different hobbies: cooking, camping, dancing, fishing
1. the person who's hobby is camping is on the far left##1
2. the person drinking lemonade is on the right of the person drinking cola##1
3. the person who's hobby is cooking is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is camping##3
4. the person drinking cola is on the right of the person drinking mirinda##1
5. the person who's hobby is fishing is the person drinking sprite##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |   1    |    2    |       3       |      4      |
| Beverage   | mirinda    | cola   | lemonade | sprite    |
| Hobby      | camping | cooking | dancing       | fishing |

