3. the person driving the skateboard is between the person driving the scooter and the person drinking lemonade##2
4. the person driving the bus is on the far right##1
5. the person drinking water is on the left or right of the person drinking milk##3

.:: Answer ::.
|             |   1    |   2   |    3     |   4   |
| Beverage    | lemonade | mirinda | milk | water |
| Transport   | jet-ski | skateboard  | scooter    | bus  |

