2. the person who's hobby is collecting is the person watching comedy movies##1
3. the person who's hobby is collecting is on the left of the person watching animation movies##1
4. the person who's hobby is collecting is on the left of the person who's hobby is woodworking##1
5. the person who's hobby is cooking is on the left of the person who's hobby is traveling##1
6. the person watching comedy movies is on the left or right of the person watching animation movies##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2      |      3      |     4     |
| Hobby         | collecting | woodworking | cooking | traveling   |
| Movie-Genre   | comedy | animation | thriller      | satire |

