2. the person who's sport is baseball is on the far right##1
3. the person who's sport is baseball is the owner of the frog##1
4. the owner of the ferret is on the left of the owner of the rabbit##1
5. the owner of the ferret is on the far left or far right##3
6. the owner of the rabbit is between the person who's sport is rowing and the person who's sport is swimming##2

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1      |   2    |     3      |     4      |
| Pet     | ferret | rabbit   | rat      | frog      |
| Sport   | rowing     | climbing | swimming | baseball |

