.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-11::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: cooking, hiking, photography, fishing
The people use 4 different means of transport: bike, subway, car, ship
1. the person who's hobby is hiking is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is fishing##3
2. the person who's hobby is hiking is on the right of the person driving the subway##1
3. the person driving the ship is the person who's hobby is photography##1
4. the person who's hobby is photography is on the left or right of the person driving the car##3
5. the person driving the ship is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is cooking##3
6. the person driving the car is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |     2      |     3      |     4      |
| Hobby       | cooking | photography | fishing    | hiking      |
| Transport   | car       | ship       | subway | bike |

