.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-13::.
There are 4 different nationalities: thai, pakistani, mexican, japanese
4 different pets are kept: lizard, ferret, chinchilla, hedgehog
1. the pakistani is on the far right##1
2. the thai is the thai##1
3. the owner of the ferret is on the left or right of the owner of the lizard##3
4. the owner of the lizard is on the left or right of the pakistani##3
5. the mexican is on the left or right of the japanese##3
6. the owner of the ferret is on the left or right of the japanese##3
7. the owner of the lizard is on the right of the owner of the hedgehog##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2    |    3    |    4     |
| Nationality   | thai | mexican  | japanese | pakistani |
| Pet           | chinchilla     | hedgehog | lizard    | ferret     |

