.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-14::.
There 4 different types of food: lime, tomato, broccoli, corn
The people have 4 different jobs:  photographer, software-developer, entrepreneur, police-officer
1. the person eating corn is on the left or right of the software-developer##3
2. the software-developer is on the right of the entrepreneur##1
3. the person eating tomato is on the left of the photographer##1
4. the software-developer is on the far left or far right##3
5. the person eating broccoli is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|        |    1     |     2     |    3    |     4     |
| Food   | tomato  | lime | corn  | broccoli      |
| Job    | police-officer | photographer | entrepreneur | software-developer |

