.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-15::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: skydiving, puzzles, video-games, chess
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: disco, blues, house, hip-hop
1. the person who's hobby is skydiving is on the far right##1
2. the fan of blues is on the left of the fan of house##1
3. the person who's hobby is puzzles is the fan of hip-hop##1
4. the fan of blues is the person who's hobby is video-games##1
5. the fan of house is on the left or right of the fan of blues##3
6. the fan of house is the person who's hobby is skydiving##1
7. the fan of blues is on the left or right of the fan of disco##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |       2       |    3    |     4      |
| Hobby         | puzzles | chess | video-games | skydiving |
| Music-Genre   | hip-hop     | disco       | blues   | house      |

