.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-20::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: juice, 7up, sprite, almond-milk
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: surfing, biathlon, skateboarding, parkour
1. the person who's sport is skateboarding is on the far right##1
2. the person who's sport is parkour is the person who's sport is parkour##1
3. the person drinking almond-milk is on the left or right of the person who's sport is parkour##3
4. the person who's sport is surfing is on the far left or far right##3
5. the person who's sport is parkour is on the left or right of the person who's sport is skateboarding##3
6. the person who's sport is surfing is on the left of the person drinking juice##1
7. the person drinking sprite is on the left or right of the person who's sport is skateboarding##3

.:: Answer ::.
|            |     1     |    2     |       3       |    4     |
| Beverage   | 7up     | juice     | sprite          | almond-milk |
| Sport      | surfing | biathlon | parkour | skateboarding  |

 